#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: backup
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `backup`;

CREATE TABLE `backup` (
  `id_backup` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `tgl` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT current_timestamp() ON UPDATE current_timestamp(),
  `file` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id_backup`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: cp_kinerja
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `cp_kinerja`;

CREATE TABLE `cp_kinerja` (
  `idCapai` int(255) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `idOpd` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `kd` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `program` text DEFAULT NULL,
  `indikator` text DEFAULT NULL,
  `satuan` text DEFAULT NULL,
  `target` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `real_target` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `alokasi_ang` bigint(20) DEFAULT 0,
  `real_ang` bigint(20) DEFAULT 0,
  `presentasi` bigint(20) DEFAULT 0,
  `permasalahan` text DEFAULT NULL,
  `upaya` text DEFAULT NULL,
  `tl` text DEFAULT NULL,
  `p_id` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `tahun` year(4) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`idCapai`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=110 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: is_program
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `is_program`;

CREATE TABLE `is_program` (
  `id_isProg` int(255) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `kdProg` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `nmProg` text NOT NULL,
  `p_id` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `tahun` year(4) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id_isProg`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: isian_urusan
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `isian_urusan`;

CREATE TABLE `isian_urusan` (
  `id_isian_urusan` int(255) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `kdUrus` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `nmUrus` text NOT NULL,
  `tahun` year(4) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id_isian_urusan`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=2 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: kegiatan
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `kegiatan`;

CREATE TABLE `kegiatan` (
  `idKeg` int(255) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `kdKeg` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `nmKeg` text NOT NULL,
  `p_id` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`idKeg`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=473 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: kontak
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `kontak`;

CREATE TABLE `kontak` (
  `id_kontak` varchar(11) NOT NULL,
  `nama` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `telepon` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `alamat` text NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id_kontak`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: pengaturan
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `pengaturan`;

CREATE TABLE `pengaturan` (
  `id_pengaturan` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `nama_aplikasi` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `logo` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `smtp_host` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `smtp_email` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `smtp_username` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `smtp_password` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `smtp_port` int(11) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id_pengaturan`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=2 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: role
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `role`;

CREATE TABLE `role` (
  `id_role` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `nama_role` varchar(30) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id_role`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=4 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

INSERT INTO `role` (`id_role`, `nama_role`) VALUES (1, 'Admin');
INSERT INTO `role` (`id_role`, `nama_role`) VALUES (3, 'opd');


#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: subkegiatan
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `subkegiatan`;

CREATE TABLE `subkegiatan` (
  `idSubkeg` int(255) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `kdSubkeg` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `nmSubkeg` text NOT NULL,
  `kinerja` text DEFAULT NULL,
  `indikator` text DEFAULT NULL,
  `satuan` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `p_id` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`idSubkeg`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=2315 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: token_user
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `token_user`;

CREATE TABLE `token_user` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `id_user` char(10) NOT NULL,
  `tgl` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT current_timestamp(),
  `token` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: urusan
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `urusan`;

CREATE TABLE `urusan` (
  `idUrus` int(255) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `kdUrus` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `nmUrus` text NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`idUrus`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=9 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: user
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `user`;

CREATE TABLE `user` (
  `id_user` char(10) NOT NULL,
  `nama_user` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `alamat` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `jk` enum('L','P') NOT NULL,
  `telepon` char(12) NOT NULL,
  `email` varchar(30) NOT NULL,
  `password` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `gambar` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `id_role` int(11) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id_user`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;
